 said tomer frey chief technology officer and senior vice president of product at wisertogether wisertogethers personalization is driven by the companys unique consumer health preferences knowledge base with over four million consumer treatment decisions and growing rapidly the database powers the wiser health solution and helps consumers focus on treatments best suited to their concerns values and preferences and to engage in productive and informed conversations with their medical providers as technology advances consumers are becoming more familiar with digital services and devices catering to the users personalized preferences and values personalization diminishes the onesizefitsall approach to health care and boosts the consumers participation and ownership over their health and outcomes enabling health care consumers to become active participants in their health increases their overall satisfaction and compliance with their treatment said shub debgupta ceo of wisertogether by marrying personalization and health care in a scalable way wisertogether is at the forefront of the consumerism and patientcentric revolution underway in healthcare by engaging users as unique individuals and helping them make better shared decisions wisertogether helps achieve better health outcomes lowers costs and improves satisfaction added mr debgupta about wisertogether incwisertogethers personalized healthcare treatment comparison software enables consumers to choose the right treatment – most effective in outcome most personally suitable and most costeffective and affordable the result is improved health and improved costs for consumers their employers payers and providers the company serves over  million people through their employers and health plans for more information about wisertogether please visit our website at wwwwisertogethercom wisertogether contact catherine riedelcatherinenextleveleverythingcom  source wisertogether inc related links httpwwwwisertogethercom view tabl