her inc provides shared decisionmaking tools to consumers employers health plans payers and providers its decisionmaking tools enable consumers to achieve better health outcomes and employers health plans and payers to save money the company offers wiser health a personalized decisionmaking tool that assesses possible treatments and helps consumers to determine the best option for them based on various factors including clinical evidence personal and popular preferences cost and coverage wiser health mail a hypertargeted message that helps clients to engage consumers in their own health care decisions and wiser health social that uses social media to continuously engage consumers on their health and wellness decisions it offers its solutions in various health areas including musculoskeletal and cardiovascular conditions diabetes mental health pregnancy and respiratory illnesses wisertogether inc was founded in  and is based in washington district of columbia with an additional office in boston massachusetts detailed description  thomas jefferson street nwwashington dc united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwwisertogethercom key executives for wisertogether inc dr shub debgupta founder and chief executive officer mr praveen v mooganur founder and chief operating officer mr david e ehrhardt chief financial officer mr erik labianca chief architect  security officer dr james h herndon md mba chief medical officer and member of medical advisory board compensation as of fiscal year  wisertogether inc key developments wisertogether  inc relaunches its healthcare treatment platform for its enterprise clients and their employees members and patients apr   wisertogether announced a relaunch of its healthcare treatment platform for its enterprise clients and their employees members and patients the new solution return to health® also introduced as a mobile app empowers health consumers to improve their decisionmaking leading to greater adherence and decreased cost return to health® integrates clinical guidelines exclusive consumer preference ratings cost transparency and return to health timeline data with the specific condition and attributes of the user the solution synthesizes this vast array of data into best good and poor treatment categories enabling the individual to understand act and adhere to the most appropriate next step on their road to improved health wisertogethers return to health® automates the steps necessary to act on their treatment choices and facilitates a true shared decision process with their provider the return to health® platform was launched in january  and half of the wisertogether client base has already chosen to launch the enhanced tool clients who have implemented are seeing an average increase of  in their populations utilization and engagement benezon adopts wisertogethers wisercoach to educate members and drive healthcare transparency mar   wisertogether announced that wisertogethers wisercoach solution is now being utilized by benezon with the wisercoach solution benezon subject matter experts smes can access and utilize wisertogethers wiser health tool a decision support solution focused on datadriven and evidencebased treatment transparency to help educate members on questions to ask their doctor and treatment options that meet their personal preferences improving productivity for plan members and reducing costs for benezon clients and customers dominion resources adopts wisertogether platform to improve health care decisionmaking for employees jan   wisertogether inc announced that dominion resources inc will offer wiser health to its employees and their dependents the companys wiser health product is a treatment decisionsupport solution that provides health consumers with comprehensive information on prevalent medical conditions and treatments the wiser health solution brings together clinical evidence and patient preference data in an innovative personalized consumer experience that can readily i